        "description": "Based in <span class='highlight-text-primary'>Jizzax, Uzbekistan</span>; creating content, building projects, and sharing knowledge through <span class='highlight-text-secondary'>blogging and coding</span>, with a focus on <span class='highlight-text-tertiary'>practical solutions</span>.",
        "full": "I'm Zarifjon A'zamov — an IT Blogger and Developer from Jizzax, Uzbekistan. I'm passionate about technology, programming, and sharing knowledge with the community through my blog and social media channels.<br/><br/>I create educational content about programming, tech trends, and software development on Telegram, Instagram, and YouTube under the brand AZAMOV. My goal is to make technology accessible and understandable for Uzbek-speaking audiences.<br/><br/>On the development side, I work with modern web technologies including React, Next.js, Node.js, and various other tools. I enjoy building practical applications that solve real-world problems.<br/><br/>I believe in learning by doing — every project teaches something new, and sharing that knowledge multiplies its value. Whether it's a blog post, a video, or a code project, I aim to deliver quality content that genuinely helps people.<br/><br/>My current focus is growing the AZAMOV brand, creating more educational tech content, and building open-source projects for the community.",
